## Theory Behind GLM. Generalized Linear modeeling. Why use binomial as a glm family decide whether the email is spam (1) or not (0). In this post, we call the model “binomial logistic regression”, since the variable to predict is binary, however, logistic regression can also be used to predict a dependent variable which can assume more than 2 values. In this second case, we call the model “multinomial logistic regression”. A typical example, for instance, would be classifying films between “Entertaining”, “borderline” or “boring”.

ref nice theory
